✨ CONSISTENCY FIX: Page Background Panel Icons

Replace emoji icons with Font Awesome icons to achieve visual consistency
with Section Editor's background options.

## Changes

### Page Background Type Selector
- Color: 🎨 → fa-solid fa-palette
- Gradient: 🌈 → fa-solid fa-brush
